  "title": "Food Manufacturing Associates",
  "description": "<p>Suitable For Primary, Secondary, ITE, Diploma and Degree Holders, fresh graduate / 1 to 3 years working experience of all fields, with or without F&B experience.</p><p>Willing to join a SME.</p><p>A person that is driven, adaptable, independent and willing to learn in a very different environment and culture. A great problem solver and initiator in a very broad sets of challenges. Embrace change with new technology.</p><p>We offer competitive salary, benefits, full basic expenses and coverage. </p><p>The Job Scope encompass the following:</p><p>1.    Manage factory operations & ensuring smooth operations</p><p>2.    Preparation of desserts, ice creams and beverages ingredients according to SOP</p><p>3.    Processing of desserts, ice creams and beverages</p><p>4.    Housekeeping duties such as sweeping, mopping, washing and cleaning.</p><p>5.    Ensuring a neat, clean, hygienic & tidy workplace at all times</p><p>6.    Verify stock delivery and inventory management</p><p>Interested candidates please send in your full resume to info@conutink.com</p><p>Please refer to our website for more details about our organisation:</p><p><a href=\"http://www.conutink.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.conutink.com</a></p><p></p>",
